data.description: This lovely stunning corner lot home is move in ready with freshly painted interior walls. It comes with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath,  1/2 bath downstair and 1 car garage. The refrigerator, washer, dryer, reverse osmosis, tankless, water softener, extra water line with hot water in the backyard are included.  Backyard is well done with synthetic grass and pavers for less maintenance. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property yours and start living the life you've always dreamed of.
